meaningMnemonic: <kanji>Rent</kanji> it and I will <kanji>lend</kanji> it to you. This thing that is being lent and rented? It's a <vocabulary>rental</vocabulary>.
readingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word that uses the on'yomi readings of the kanji. You just have to remember that 貸 is read as たい for this one. What is your rental? It is a <reading>tie</reading> (たい) fighter. Sweet.
